Key Match Events: Travis d'Arnaud hit a walk-off home run for the Braves
Pre-Game Insights: The Braves entered the week two games behind both the Mets and D-backs in the NL Wild Card race
Post-Match Reflections: The Braves can clinch a postseason berth with either a win over the Royals on Sunday, or a D-backs loss to the Padres

Others: The Braves' rotation is considered the best since manager Brian Snitker has been a manager
